42
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:39,870
Mother.

43
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:44,000
Yanwen.

44
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,560
Mother.

45
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:45,750
Xianlan.

46
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:46,750
Sister.

47
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:49,360
Is Lady Wang still sick?

48
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,280
Yes.

49
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:51,470
She's still got a bit of a cough,

50
