and fulfill my filial duty.

64
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,610
Why isn't Yanyun here yet?

65
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,200
Didn't they just say he was on his way?

66
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:31,310
Where is your Master?

67
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,240
Old Madam,

68
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,630
Third Master has gone to Baoxiang Temple.

69
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,120
He asked the Old Madam, Second Madam,

70
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,650
