The whole family has been waiting for him.

76
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:54,280
Yanyun has been
the Grand Secretary for so long.

77
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,410
He's used to having people wait on him.

78
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,120
But it's not right
to keep Xianlan waiting.

79
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,790
It's not about right or wrong.

80
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,150
We are family.

81
