92
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,300
I'll change my clothes and be right over.

93
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,070
Alright.

94
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,070
To bring down Fan Chuan,

95
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,690
he actually went so far

96
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,360
