101
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,159
It only shows that

102
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:57,000
when someone as capable as mentor

103
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,530
becomes absorbed in power,

104
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:01,320
the harm they can cause is a hundred

105
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:04,080
or even a thousand times greater than that

106
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,790
of those without talent.

107
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:14,330
I came to understand it
while I was in prison.

108
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,290
Neither Fan Chuan, Wang Xuanfan,

109
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,750
or my mentor,

110
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,030
are my kind of people.

111
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:21,510
But

112
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:23,600
