116
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,000
Yes.

117
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,830
The path ahead of me

118
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:33,290
will certainly be difficult.

119
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,510
What do you mean?

120
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:38,740
Are you trying to persuade me
to stay away from you?

121
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,240
What are you panicking for?

122
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,570
I'm not clinging to you.

123
