In that case,

157
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,220
if I ever run into danger

158
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,840
at court in the future,

159
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:53,510
you can

160
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,940
take this,

161
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,290
