164
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,000
Or,

165
00:08:01,970 --> 00:08:03,230
if you grow tired of me,

166
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,390
you can use it too.

167
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,530
You just came up with this

168
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,950
while you were

169
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,460
in the Penal Court prison?

170
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,040
What do you think?

171
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,560
You seek neither

172
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:17,760
wealth nor fame.

173
00:08:18,550 --> 00:08:20,610
What you fear is losing your freedom.

174
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,900
I am also afraid

175
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,730
