179
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:33,299
Your three-year mourning period is over.

180
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,260
I wrote two copies.

181
00:08:36,220 --> 00:08:37,440
I plan to

182
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:39,030
