206
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:53,360
Grand Secretary is really something.

207
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,760
He's different from

208
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,240
ordinary people like us.

209
00:09:56,610 --> 00:09:58,680
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

210
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,430
You don't seek

211
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,440
wealth or fame.

212
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,380
What you fear is losing your freedom.

213
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,610
I am also afraid

214
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,510
that a slight misstep in the future

215
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,710
