216
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:15,470
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

217
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,480
If I ever run into danger

218
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,320
at court in the future,

219
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:16,840
you can

220
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,150
take this,

221
00:10:18,630 --> 00:10:19,560
fill in the date,

222
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,460
and leave without

223
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:22,920
having to consult anyone.

224
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:24,510
Or

225
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,770
if you grow tired of me,

226
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,960
you can use it too.

227
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:35,020
May you, after this parting,

228
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,930
have a bright future,

229
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,850
radiant as the morning sun,

230
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:41,050
with all things going your way

231
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,480
and a life of ease and joy.

232
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:08,320
What?

233
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:10,060
You want me to pay?

234
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:12,750
Our Gu family has suffered
a great disaster this time.

235
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:13,550
All the men in the family

236
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,200
were thrown into prison.

237
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:17,440
This whole disaster

238
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,550
was brought about by

239
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:20,270
your dereliction of duty.

240
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,080
It's only right that your branch

241
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,480
bears the compensation.

242
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:25,320
What do you mean I caused it?

243
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,730
I was framed

244
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,320
by Sun Shitao.

245
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,200
I'm wronged too.

246
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,000
You're wronged?

247
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,840
You are the Director of the Treasury.

248
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,510
12,000 tons of grain from

249
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,320
the Daxin granary were switched out.

250
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,790
They used your seal,

251
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,600
and you didn't even know!

252
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,640
You still claim you're wronged?

253
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,170
Who do you think
is more wronged—you or me?

254
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,600
I have worked hard

255
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,510
in the Censorate for so many years,

256
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:55,370
finally getting a chance to rise.

257
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,590
If it weren't for you,

258
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,760
I'd already have been promoted.

259
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,480
And now

260
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:05,840
who knows how long
I'll have to wait again.

261
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,910
Exactly.

262
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,510
He was thrown into prison for nothing.

263
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:11,630
That's hardly a good reputation to have.

264
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:12,290
He may never

265
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,510
get another chance because of this.

266
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,360
Will you stop

267
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,750
jinxing it?

268
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,630
Dezhao.

269
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:27,690
Deyuan suffered this time

270
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,400
purely because of you.

271
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:31,240
He was just collateral damage.

272
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:33,040
If you know what's proper,

273
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,270
you should bring out some silver

274
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:36,120
to compensate the second branch,

275
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,000
and let this matter

276
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,840
end here.

277
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:40,280
I can't.

278
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,960
I've already been

279
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:44,490
exiled to some godforsaken place

280
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:47,130
as a petty seventh-grade official.

281
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,290
And you still want me

282
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:51,600
to give money to them?

283
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,620
You might as well ask me to die.

284
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,000
My Lady.

285
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:12,120
My Lady,

286
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,800
you're finally back.

287
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,490
My Lady.

288
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,510
Your branch

289
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:18,120
has made our whole family suffer so much.

290
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,510
I just took a few of your things,

291
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:21,060
and you're stopping me?

292
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,530
And you dare to scold me?

293
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,150
Someone!

294
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,120
Take everything

295
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,240
from those shelves!

296
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,120
Yes, My Lady.

297
00:13:27,210 --> 00:13:27,980
Get up.

298
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:29,970
You, go over there.

299
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,080
No.

300
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:32,780
No!

301
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,940
Don't touch it!

302
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,510
Don't!

303
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:38,240
-You can't take this!
-My Lady.

304
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:39,880
You can't take this!

305
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,120
My mother gave this to me!

306
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,100
Give it

307
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,150
back to me!

308
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:58,200
I'll beat you to death!

309
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,910
Are you crazy?

310
00:14:00,460 --> 00:14:01,700
Yes, I am crazy.

311
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,190
What are you doing?

312
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:06,510
Mother!

313
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:07,200
My Lady.

314
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,840
You wretch!

315
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:11,750
Mother, she scratched my face

316
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:13,640
and tried to strangle me!

317
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:15,600
You little wrech!

318
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,000
Being raised by a concubine

319
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,550
has made you utterly vicious.

320
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:19,810
You're truly malicious.

321
00:14:19,810 --> 00:14:20,720
Someone!

322
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,510
Seize her!

323
00:14:21,810 --> 00:14:22,360
Yes.

324
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,320
Mother.

325
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,030
She was trying to kill me!

326
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:25,670
My Lady.

327
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,930
Let go of my lady!

328
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,270
-Don't hit her.
-I'll teach you!

329
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:30,200
Don't you dare hit her!

330
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,830
-Stop!
-You wrech!

331
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,910
You think you're tough, huh?

332
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:34,630
Stop!

333
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:37,230
Let her go!

334
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,440
Don't let her go.

335
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:40,670
She hit Lian.

336
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,910
She can't go.

337
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:42,660
Qingpu!

338
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,390
Yes!

339
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:51,930
Zhao.

340
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:54,150
Lian wanted to take my things.

341
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:54,870
I refused,

342
00:14:55,070 --> 00:14:56,270
so she snatched them.

343
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,800
What do you mean "snatched"?

344
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:58,960
You're the ones

345
00:14:58,960 --> 00:14:59,750
who owe us.

346
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:01,670
Owe you?

347
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:03,870
Second Aunt,

348
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,510
what does that mean?

349
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:08,080
This disaster in the household

350
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,200
was all caused by you.

351
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,630
Our second and fifth branches

352
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:13,290
were just collateral damage.

353
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:15,490
You should compensate us.

354
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,450
Compensate?

355
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:18,800
Old Madam has already agreed to it.

356
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,030
In that case,

357
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:22,420
we might as well talk it out

358
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,870
in front of Grandmother.

359
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:33,670
Does it hurt?

360
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:34,960
Can you still go?

361
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:36,790
I can.

362
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,700
I will go with you.

363
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:40,790
They've gone too far.

364
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:43,040
Let's go.

365
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,290
What are you looking at?

366
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:54,600
Since Zhao wants

367
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,900
to lay everything out at once,

368
00:15:58,030 --> 00:15:59,000
then let's do it.

369
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,850
Dexiu is on duty.

370
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,600
Rong and Xian

371
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,660
are at the academy.

372
00:16:03,910 --> 00:16:05,970
There's no need for them to come back.

373
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,430
Even though the Gu family

374
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,930
has been struck by this unjust disaster,

375
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,720
it ultimately comes down to

376
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,980
Dezhao's dereliction

377
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,150
of duty.

378
00:16:16,270 --> 00:16:17,840
You can't say that.

379
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:18,960
Dezhao.

380
00:16:20,170 --> 00:16:22,480
Let Mother finish speaking first.

381
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:27,140
We've already reached an agreement.

382
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,840
This time, the fourth branch

383
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:31,170
must compensate 100,000 taels of silver.

384
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,360
Zhao.

385
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:34,370
Although you are a junior,

386
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:37,200
everyone knows you in charge
of the fourth branch.

387
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,550
What's your view on this?

388
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:39,950
100,000 taels of silver?

389
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,390
Our entire household's annual income

390
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:44,850
is just over 20,000 taels.

391
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:47,840
And you're asking
for 100,000 just like that?

392
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:50,760
Do you really think I have mountains
of gold and silver?

393
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:52,240
You can't say that.

394
00:16:52,650 --> 00:16:54,560
We suffered a huge loss this time.

395
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,200
Your Second Uncle

396
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:56,750
was originally about to

397
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,750
become Vice Minister of Personnel.

398
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:03,630
Second Uncle won't be able to
become Vice Minister of Personnel.

399
00:17:04,589 --> 00:17:05,240
Why?

400
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:07,800
Because Lord Yao Ping

401
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:08,950
also wants the post.

402
00:17:09,609 --> 00:17:11,349
He has followed
the Senior Grand Secretary for many years

403
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,609
and ranks ahead of you.

404
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:13,349
What...

405
00:17:14,170 --> 00:17:15,690
what do you know

406
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:17,050
about court politics?

407
00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:19,069
I at least

408
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,400
had a chance.

409
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:25,010
But because of the trouble Dezhao caused,

410
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:27,310
it's all gone now.

411
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:27,970
What...

412
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:30,070
what do you mean I caused the trouble?

413
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:32,870
I'm also the victim
of that unwarranted disaster.

414
00:17:38,350 --> 00:17:39,510
Do you all think

415
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,660
this case of relief grain

416
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:42,830
being replaced with bran was caused

417
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:43,640
by our master?

418
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:46,970
If so,

419
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,240
then our Gu family

420
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:50,430
will be in for another disaster.

421
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:52,590
What do you mean?

422
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,070
True.

423
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:56,440
Master is guilty of dereliction of duty.

424
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:58,590
But he has already
been convicted by the court

425
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:00,070
and demoted to
a seventh-grade county magistrate.

426
00:18:00,070 --> 00:18:01,670
The case has been concluded,

427
00:18:01,710 --> 00:18:03,180
and the court has already dropped it.

428
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,360
Now that he's home,

429
00:18:04,390 --> 00:18:06,190
why hold him accountable again?

430
00:18:07,310 --> 00:18:09,160
Are you suggesting that

431
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:11,690
His Majesty and the court were unjust,

432
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,180
and that you wish to set up your own court

433
00:18:13,180 --> 00:18:14,350
and retry the case?

434
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,550
You... you're just

435
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:18,000
being unreasonable.

436
00:18:19,350 --> 00:18:21,070
If you insist on taking this money,

437
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,550
then I'll go straight
to the Shuntian Prefecture

438
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:24,550
and have the magistrate pass judgment.

439
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:26,200
I've been there twice anyway.

440
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,000
I'm not afraid

441
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:28,290
to go there once more.

442
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:29,030
Right.

443
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:33,060
Gu Jinzhao.

444
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,570
Don't be unreasonable.

445
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:36,540
The court

446
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,550
has treated this as a state matter.

447
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:39,480
But here and now,

448
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:41,120
it is a family matter.

449
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,780
Since it's a family matter,

450
00:18:42,780 --> 00:18:44,550
it should be be settled by family rules.

451
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:46,000
Don't bring up criminal charges here.

452
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:46,400
So

453
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,240
you mean

454
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:50,110
you won't pay a single penny?

455
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:52,680
Not exactly.

456
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,470
Our master is not entirely

457
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:58,160
without fault in this matter.

458
00:18:58,620 --> 00:19:00,130
I will have someone check

459
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,480
the losses of each branch
in their shops and estates,

460
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,790
calculate a reasonable amount

461
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,240
and provide compensation accordingly.

462
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,770
I will hand it all over to you

463
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,130
for distribution.

464
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:09,850
Do any of you

465
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,200
have any objections?

466
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:18,850
Zhao's proposal is reasonable.

467
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,730
Our branch has no objections.

468
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,380
Hui should be awake by now.

469
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:23,310
Mother.

470
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:24,870
If there's nothing else,

471
00:19:24,870 --> 00:19:26,150
I'll take my leave.

472
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:31,480
You should all go now.

473
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:34,000
I should get some rest as well.

474
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,770
Wait.

475
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,720
Lian tried to take Lan's belongings

476
00:19:41,770 --> 00:19:43,200
and even smashed her

477
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,550
jade-and-gold necklace.

478
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:46,380
Shouldn't Lian compensate for that too?

479
00:19:46,380 --> 00:19:47,640
There was such a thing?

480
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:50,240
H... how much do you want?

481
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,200
That necklace

482
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,480
was recorded in the register.

483
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,210
It is worth 500 taels of silver.

484
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:58,880
500 taels?

485
00:20:00,750 --> 00:20:01,880
I'm not paying that!

486
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:03,790
If you don't want to pay, that's fine.

487
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:04,400
Later,

488
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:05,440
We can simply

489
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,720
deduct it from the silver

490
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,000
allocated to your branch.

491
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:08,590
You...

492
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:14,510
Zhao.

493
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:16,960
Then can I...

494
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:25,390
Thank you, Zhao,

495
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,210
for upholding justice for me.

496
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:29,160
I was just about to say something to you.

497
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:31,000
While I've been away,

498
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:33,170
I heard you spent money

499
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,510
to make sure

500
00:20:34,510 --> 00:20:36,310
Rong was looked after in prison.

501
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:39,070
I'm now planning
to renovate Linxia Restaurant

502
00:20:39,070 --> 00:20:39,880
and reopen it

503
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,710
as a new shop.

504
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,590
I want to expand the shares.

505
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,680
If you are willing,

506
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:45,210
you can take a stake as well.

507
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:46,370
But

508
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,750
you have to think it through.

509
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:48,730
Business always

510
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,350
comes with both profit and loss.

511
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:51,110
I'm willing.

512
00:20:52,770 --> 00:20:53,700
Thank you, Zhao.

513
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:55,820
Mother.

514
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:56,550
This...

515
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:57,980
Zhao.

516
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,980
Do you still have any shares

517
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,720
left in your Linxia Restaurant?

518
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:05,550
Right.

519
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,000
We are all family.

520
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:07,920
If there's profit to be made,

521
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,520
we should share it together.

522
00:21:10,690 --> 00:21:12,290
Share the profits together?

523
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:15,400
You really have the nerve to say that.

524
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,440
Lan, let's go.

525
00:21:35,230 --> 00:21:36,340
I'm exhausted.

526
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,920
Saying all these things

527
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,510
gave me a headache.

528
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,750
My Lady, you are too kind.

529
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:48,920
You even gave them
the properties as compensation.

530
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:49,830
Honestly,

531
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:51,240
even if you didn't pay a single penny,

532
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,300
what could they do?

533
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:54,910
They couldn't do anything to me,

534
00:21:55,420 --> 00:21:57,220
but they could annoy me to death.

535
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:01,430
Besides,

536
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:03,390
our branch

537
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:05,160
is not entirely
without fault in this matter.

538
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,290
Let's just pay them.

539
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,260
Moreover, whether they can even keep

540
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,680
this small amount of silver

541
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,210
is still another question.

542
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,310
Why?

543
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:16,060
Think about it.

544
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,530
If I marry Third Master,

545
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:18,860
would they dare

546
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:20,110
reduce my dowry?

547
00:22:20,670 --> 00:22:21,800
They wouldn't dare!

548
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:23,590
Exactly.

549
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,550
This Zhao

550
00:22:30,570 --> 00:22:31,970
is really unreasonable.

551
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,250
Lan is just a concubine-born sister.

552
00:22:35,470 --> 00:22:37,450
Why did Zhao give her shares?

553
00:22:37,470 --> 00:22:38,930
She should give them to me.

554
00:22:39,010 --> 00:22:41,080
I am her legitimate cousin.

555
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:42,240
Besides,

556
00:22:42,920 --> 00:22:45,050
I am going to marry into the Yao family.

557
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:46,040
Pleasing me

558
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,460
is much more useful than pleasing Gu Lan.

559
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,110
I'm talking to you.

560
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:53,330
Don't you think so?

561
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:54,960
Yes, My Lady.

562
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:58,310
You are not clever at all.

563
00:22:58,310 --> 00:23:00,110
-Why are you so stupid?
-My Lady.

564
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,060
You're not even close to Tang.

565
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,000
My Lady.

566
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:04,070
It hurts.

567
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,140
Isn't this Ziling?

568
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:10,960
Come here.

569
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:17,750
Well,

570
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:19,170
do you understand?

571
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,300
My Lady,

572
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,670
that won't do.

573
00:23:21,960 --> 00:23:23,230
Why not?

574
00:23:24,790 --> 00:23:26,070
If you don't do that,

575
00:23:26,590 --> 00:23:27,590
I'll have you sold off

576
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:29,320
first thing tomorrow morning.

577
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:30,590
Believe it or not.

578
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,000
It hurts.

579
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:38,350
Ziling.

580
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:40,180
C... come here.

581
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:41,440
Xiuju?

582
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,210
What are you doing here?

583
00:23:45,910 --> 00:23:47,120
I sprained my ankle.

584
00:23:47,270 --> 00:23:48,670
Can you help me up?

585
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:52,240
Let me see.

586
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,350
It hurts.

587
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,350
Is it here?

588
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,300
Over here.

589
00:23:55,550 --> 00:23:56,440
Here.

590
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,590
It hurts so much.

591
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,030
Let's go.

592
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:03,790
Let's go.

593
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:09,310
Luckily they dug out
the pond mud a few days ago,

594
00:24:09,310 --> 00:24:10,710
so the water wasn't deep.

595
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:12,670
This Gu Lian

596
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,510
is truly going too far.

597
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:15,880
Oh, right.

598
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:24,570
Good thing it didn't get soaked.

599
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:26,660
I went to three silversmith shops

600
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:27,790
before finally finding one

601
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:29,640
that could repair that necklace.

602
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,230
This is the deposit receipt.

603
00:24:31,230 --> 00:24:33,090
I'll keep it safe for you, My Lady.

604
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,450
You're still worrying about

605
00:24:36,450 --> 00:24:38,380
the deposit when you're like this?

606
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,110
All I can think about

607
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:40,720
is how to get revenge on her.

608
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,960
Yao Wenxiu

609
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:48,160
has sent another letter, hasn't he?

610
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:48,920
Yes.

611
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:51,920
Bring it to me.

612
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:01,570
He actually wants me to go admire flowers?

613
00:25:01,830 --> 00:25:03,350
He really has no shame.

614
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:05,960
Bring me

615
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,580
my writing materials later.

616
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:11,110
My Lady, are you going
to meet Young Master Yao?

617
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:11,550
Yes.

618
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,000
But

619
00:25:14,510 --> 00:25:15,200
Young Master Yao

620
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:17,240
is Miss Lian's future husband.

621
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,060
That's exactly why I'm going.

622
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:23,030
Well...

623
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:24,550
I'll go get them then.

624
00:25:31,010 --> 00:25:33,650
[Baiwei Restaurant]

625
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,920
What's the rush?

626
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,570
Have a drink with me?

627
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,000
Wine?

628
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:43,150
I prepared it specially for you.

629
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:45,360
I heard you like Zhaoyebai.

630
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,000
Alright.

631
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,240
You prepared it for me,

632
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:51,040
yet you started drinking first.

633
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,030
Come on.

634
00:26:06,200 --> 00:26:06,920
Not bad.

635
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:12,280
You've been to the file storeroom?

636
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:14,410
It was quite an eye-opener.

637
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,270
Did you read the ones

638
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:17,760
bearing my name?

639
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:18,750
Yes.

640
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:20,270
The file storeroom

641
00:26:20,270 --> 00:26:22,240
contains 167 iron chests

642
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,700
of surveillance records.

643
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,350
Among all the court's
senior officials,

644
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:26,590
some have one or two chests,

645
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,120
some have more than a dozen.

646
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,980
But there is one person

647
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:31,130
who has none at all.

648
00:26:32,550 --> 00:26:33,400
Fu Hailian.

649
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,150
If I'm not mistaken,

650
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:37,790
after His Majesty ascended the throne,

651
00:26:37,820 --> 00:26:39,640
he ordered Zhang Ling
to secretly destroy them.

652
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,000
Have you interrogated Zhang Ling?

653
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,730
Every form of torture was used,

654
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:45,730
but he refused to confess
even a single word.

655
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:48,720
I want the leverage

656
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,120
you hold over Fu Hailian.

657
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:51,640
Since you have information about

658
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,310
Zhao Jichang

659
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:54,270
bribing court officials
from more than ten years ago,

660
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,640
you must also have something on him.

661
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,240
I don't have any.

662
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,040
You're lying.

663
00:26:57,900 --> 00:26:59,160
I really don't have it.

664
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:00,730
Even if I did,

665
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,500
it wouldn't prove anything.

666
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:03,890
Think about it.

667
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:05,030
If I had known

668
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,790
about his crimes,

669
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:07,830
why would I have

670
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,290
followed him until today?

671
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,590
So you regret it now?

672
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:13,970
Not exactly.

673
00:27:14,520 --> 00:27:15,550
Anyone in his position

674
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,920
may not necessarily

675
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,680
have done better.

676
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,030
I know you hate him

677
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:24,490
for framing the Marquis
and the Marquisate,

678
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:26,440
so you want to find leverage

679
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,440
to bring him down.

680
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,810
But now is not the time.

681
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,640
Fan Chuan is dead.

682
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,270
Mentor holds immense power.

683
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:34,310
From the Emperor down to the ministers,

684
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:35,070
no one dares

685
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:36,440
speak against him.

686
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,040
If you go against him now,

687
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,720
you stand no chance.

688
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:44,950
You are afraid of him?

689
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:49,000
I am.

690
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,000
So,

691
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:54,070
I advise you

692
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,920
not to act rashly.

693
00:28:02,170 --> 00:28:04,650
[Generations of Excellence]

694
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,710
Give this contract

695
00:28:06,830 --> 00:28:07,980
and the account book

696
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:09,040
to Grandmother.

697
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:11,240
The distribution of silver for the second

698
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,300
and fifth branches

699
00:28:12,350 --> 00:28:13,950
has all been recorded there.

700
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,030
Yes.

701
00:28:18,750 --> 00:28:19,750
Honestly,

702
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,830
you are the most wronged in all this.

703
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,130
It was clearly Master's fault,

704
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:27,070
but you have to bear it all.

705
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:29,730
Then what else could I do?

706
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:31,420
With such a huge incident,

707
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,970
if I didn't take responsibility for it,

708
00:28:32,970 --> 00:28:34,400
the entire family,

709
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,540
including myself,

710
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:36,850
would be in trouble.

711
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:40,080
Although this incident

712
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:42,950
is ultimately the Imperial Court's fault,

713
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:44,510
if our Master

714
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:46,510
had not been so negligent in his duties,

715
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:48,510
others would not have targeted him,

716
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,730
and things

717
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,530
might not have come to this.

718
00:29:00,190 --> 00:29:02,570
[Land Survey Register]

719
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,550
Zhao is quite impressive.

720
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,880
She's more reasonable than her father.

721
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,110
Exactly.

722
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:10,240
If she'd kept being unreasonable,

723
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:12,700
we couldn't have forced
the money out of her.

724
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:16,590
Mother.

725
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,720
One of these shops

726
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:20,570
is in Dazhanmao Alley, and the other

727
00:29:20,570 --> 00:29:21,890
is near Xiaodongmen.

728
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:25,110
How about our branch

729
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:26,920
takeing the one in Xiaodongmen?

730
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:29,350
I happen to have a dowry property

731
00:29:29,350 --> 00:29:30,290
there,

732
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:32,750
so it will be more convenient to manage.

733
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,490
I was just about to say that.

734
00:29:37,270 --> 00:29:38,870
The property in Xiaodongmen

735
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:41,930
is more valuable than
the one in Dazhanmao Alley.

736
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,100
If I give it to your branch,

737
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:46,880
the fifth branch definitely won't agree.

738
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,920
If it were the other way around,

739
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:48,850
would you agree?

740
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,560
I've thought it through.

741
00:29:53,510 --> 00:29:55,500
Let's keep it in the common fund for now,

742
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:58,030
and when there's a surplus
at the end of the year,

743
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:59,430
we'll divide it equally.

744
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,750
Alright, put it away.

745
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,270
Yes, Mother.

746
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:20,680
This is

747
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,680
stinginess

748
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,080
taken to the extreme.

749
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,070
This was clearly compensation

750
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,400
from Zhao to our branch.

751
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:29,340
On what grounds is she keeping it?

752
00:30:30,350 --> 00:30:32,210
She talks nicely about letting me

753
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,500
manage the household,

754
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:36,220
but she won't let go of any control.

755
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:37,960
And your father

756
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,960
always does whatever she says.

757
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:43,350
It's driving me crazy.

758
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:46,310
Mother.

759
00:30:49,080 --> 00:30:50,350
Right now,

760
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:51,590
all I hope for is that

761
00:30:51,590 --> 00:30:53,650
you'll marry into the Yao family soon

762
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:56,400
and become the daughter-in-law
of a third-rank official.

763
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,760
Then I can finally

764
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:00,080
enjoy some prestige

765
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:01,470
and hold my head high.

766
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:03,990
Don't worry, Mother.

767
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:05,750
After I get married,

768
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:07,440
I'll come see you often

769
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,350
and back you up.

770
00:31:09,790 --> 00:31:10,920
In your dreams.

771
00:31:11,490 --> 00:31:12,790
What family lets a new bride

772
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:13,680
go back to her mother's home

773
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,810
every other day?

774
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:16,780
Wenxiu dotes on me so much.

775
00:31:16,810 --> 00:31:17,720
He even said

776
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,400
he'll do

777
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,860
whatever I say from now on.

778
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,550
Silly girl.

779
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,280
Let's go.

780
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,870
My Lady,

781
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,030
how about we...

782
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,310
Don't try to stop me anymore.

783
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:31,640
Lian has gone too far.

784
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:33,200
If I don't teach her a lesson,

785
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,510
she'll drive me crazy.

786
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,510
My Lady.

787
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,160
Lan.

788
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:44,940
I had planned to come early

789
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:46,000
and wait for you,

790
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,070
but I didn't expect

791
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:48,110
to still be late.

792
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,480
Young Master Yao.

793
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:52,290
I told you.

794
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,410
Don't call me that.

795
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,510
Wenxiu.

796
00:31:58,720 --> 00:31:59,790
Your dress today

797
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,750
is so beautiful.

798
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,960
I didn't expect you to reply so quickly.

799
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,720
I thought it would be like before—

800
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,640
no reply at all.

801
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:10,750
Actually,

802
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:12,200
I hadn't intended to come today.

803
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:12,920
Why?

804
00:32:13,450 --> 00:32:14,110
Why play dumb

805
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,970
when you know exactly what I mean?

806
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,890
You are Lian's future husband,

807
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:19,410
yet you keep writing to me

808
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,570
and inviting me to admire flowers.

809
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:23,650
But you still came, didn't you?

810
00:32:25,750 --> 00:32:26,480
Don't worry,

811
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,880
I don't like Lian.

812
00:32:31,280 --> 00:32:32,480
Don't talk nonsense.

813
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,680
I mean it.

814
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:36,110
So what?

815
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,970
You still have to marry her.

816
00:32:41,970 --> 00:32:43,730
Are you jealous?

817
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,880
You smell so lovely—

818
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:52,480
far sweeter than these flowers.

819
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:55,110
You... don't be like this.

820
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:55,930
Alright.

821
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,440
I won't tease you anymore.

822
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,070
Dear Lan.

823
00:32:58,790 --> 00:32:59,850
Since you are here,

824
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:02,080
it means you still have me in your heart.

825
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:03,440
I'll tell you the truth.

826
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:05,490
I plan to end my engagement

827
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,060
with Lian.

828
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:08,590
What?

829
00:33:09,010 --> 00:33:11,340
You are going to break off the engagement?

830
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:13,200
In a couple of days,
my mother will go to your family

831
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:15,260
to discuss it with your grandmother.

832
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:16,860
Why?

833
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,750
I never wanted to
marry her in the first place.

834
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:19,880
She always throws tantrums.

835
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,400
I really can't be bothered.

836
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,000
I've brought it up
at home several times already.

837
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,860
My parents couldn't persuade me,

838
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,490
so they finally agreed.

839
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,110
That way,

840
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,160
we can...

841
00:33:37,110 --> 00:33:38,400
I still have a zither

842
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,890
to pick up at Siming Hall.

843
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:41,110
I need to go get it now.

844
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:42,110
Please excuse me.

845
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,670
Ziling, let's go.

846
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:46,240
Lan!

847
00:33:49,590 --> 00:33:51,850
My Lady, why are you leaving so suddenly?

848
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,000
The Yao family

849
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,220
is going to break off
the engagement with Lian.

850
00:33:54,220 --> 00:33:55,950
What's the point of me staying?

851
00:33:57,450 --> 00:33:59,110
Yao Wenxiu that lying bastard

852
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:00,270
is full of nonsense.

853
00:34:00,510 --> 00:34:01,960
He said he disliked Lian,

854
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,720
so the Yao family agreed
to call off the engagement.

855
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:05,240
But the real reason is that

856
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:06,180
my Second Uncle

857
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,310
was imprisoned once

858
00:34:07,310 --> 00:34:08,909
and his career is ruined now.

859
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:11,670
Second Uncle is still
a fourth-grade official at least,

860
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:13,360
and they already look down on him.

861
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,830
Now that my father has even lost his post,

862
00:34:14,830 --> 00:34:16,690
do they still think they'd accept me?

863
00:34:16,690 --> 00:34:19,030
And yet he still had the nerve
to flirt with me.

864
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,690
You really see through it all.

865
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:23,760
Should we tell Miss Lian

866
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,780
about the Yao family
calling off the engagement?

867
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:27,110
Of course not.

868
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,550
Don't tell anyone about it.

869
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:30,150
Just wait and watch the show.

870
00:34:32,429 --> 00:34:34,670
[Chen Mansion]

871
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,330
What did you say?

872
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:37,150
You want to marry Zhao?

873
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:38,190
Yes.

874
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,280
W... why have you

875
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:42,010
suddenly decided to marry her?

876
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:45,560
Does the Gu family know?

877
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,590
What about the Ji family?

878
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:49,650
I have already informed Old Madam Ji,

879
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,230
and she has agreed.

880
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:52,449
Wait.

881
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,880
You went to Tongzhou yesterday

882
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,030
just for this?

883
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:00,870
What about Zhao?

884
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,280
Does she know?

885
00:35:02,590 --> 00:35:03,150
Yes.

886
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,170
And she has also agreed.

887
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:06,280
Right now,

888
00:35:06,590 --> 00:35:08,480
I just need your approval, Mother,

889
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,840
and I can go and propose.

890
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,070
So,

891
00:35:12,670 --> 00:35:15,100
I'm the only one you kept in the dark?

892
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:17,440
I didn't mean to keep it from you, Mother.

893
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:19,510
Of course you didn't!

894
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,920
You just didn't want

895
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:23,160
me to know too much.

896
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:26,630
You've been like this
since you were little.

897
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:28,710
People outside

898
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:30,920
only think it's glorious that
I gave birth to a son

899
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:32,580
who became a Grand Secretary.

900
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:34,880
But in fact,

901
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:37,360
you're not close

902
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,800
to me at all.

903
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,070
Mother,

904
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,320
just listen to me first.

905
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:43,150
You listen to me first!

906
00:35:45,110 --> 00:35:46,670
I really don't understand.

907
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:49,230
Why do you want to marry Zhao?

908
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:51,250
Zhao... she...

909
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,610
We all know exactly

910
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,420
what the Gu family is like.

911
00:35:56,550 --> 00:35:58,190
Zhao's reputation

912
00:35:58,190 --> 00:35:59,510
isn't good either.

913
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:02,280
She's too headstrong.

914
00:36:02,710 --> 00:36:03,920
Anyone can tell

915
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,710
that she is not someone

916
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:08,420
who will take care of the family properly.

917
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,590
She would

918
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:10,920
bring no benefit

919
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,590
to you or the Chen family.

920
00:36:12,590 --> 00:36:13,760
What I like about her

921
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,230
is that she brings me no benefit.

922
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:16,160
What do you mean?

923
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,110
You all think

924
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,000
I am the Senior Grand Secretary's

925
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,840
favorite student,

926
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,590
thriving in the court

927
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,130
and at the height of power.

928
00:36:26,550 --> 00:36:28,000
But have you ever considered—

929
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:28,840
what if one day

930
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,330
my mentor falls from power?

931
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,320
How could that be?

932
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,380
Of course it could.

933
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:38,170
No flower blooms forever.

934
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:40,440
Mentor is now immensely powerful,

935
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,510
with not a single voice
of opposition in court.

936
00:36:42,510 --> 00:36:44,550
But precisely because of that,
he is in greater danger.

937
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:45,630
Leaving everything else aside,

938
00:36:45,630 --> 00:36:46,510
His Majesty,

939
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:47,840
is growing older.

940
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,360
Sooner or later,
he will take full control of governance.

941
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:50,800
When His Majesty's authority
is fully consolidated,

942
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:51,360
think carefully—

943
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,890
who will he deal with first?

944
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,400
If that day really comes—

945
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,510
when the tree falls
and the monkeys scatter—

946
00:36:57,510 --> 00:36:59,070
what will happen

947
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:01,050
to all his followers

948
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,450
and even his family?

949
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:05,670
To call it utter ruin
would be an understatement.

950
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:06,670
So

951
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,510
you refused to marry Xue Qinglan

952
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:11,800
because of this?

953
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:12,510
Yes.

954
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:15,830
Of course, I don't like Miss Xue either.

955
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:18,370
Mentor wants me to take a side,

956
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:19,610
but I don't want to,

957
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:20,840
and I can't.

958
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,670
But you are still

959
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:24,590
the Senior Grand Secretary's student.

960
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,390
Everyone says

961
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,200
you belong to

962
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:29,250
the Fu faction.

963
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,490
That's only for now.

964
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:32,670
Do you...

965
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,000
In any case,

966
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,110
I cannot marry

967
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:40,040
the woman Mentor wants me to marry.

968
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,480
But if I marry

969
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,280
someone else,

970
00:37:42,550 --> 00:37:44,810
Mentor would definitely be displeased.

971
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:46,220
But Zhao is different.

972
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,470
First,

973
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:48,960
Mentor already knows

974
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:50,420
the Ji family works for me,

975
00:37:50,710 --> 00:37:51,230
and Zhao and I

976
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:52,510
have feelings for each other,

977
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:54,400
so he would have no grounds to object.

978
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,070
Second,

979
00:37:56,070 --> 00:37:58,550
the Chen and Ji families
are already tied by interests,

980
00:37:58,550 --> 00:38:00,030
so Zhao would not betray me.

981
00:38:00,030 --> 00:38:01,000
If I marry Zhao,

982
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:01,960
she represents

983
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:03,560
no factional power in court,

984
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:04,840
so no one

985
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,170
would feel threatened.

986
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,480
Third,

987
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,460
I like her.

988
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,640
Then naturally I must marry her.

989
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,440
After all this talk,

990
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:18,570
you are going to marry her anyway.

991
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,630
Mother.

992
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,230
Jiuheng is right.

993
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:27,230
This isn't just

994
00:38:27,230 --> 00:38:28,440
about his career.

995
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,660
It also affects our whole family.

996
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,440
Wait.

997
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:34,800
When did you start to fancy her?

998
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:37,320
You two haven't had much...

999
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:42,970
Could it be that you fell for her
at her coming-of-age ceremony?

1000
00:38:43,170 --> 00:38:44,440
No, not that soon.

1001
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:50,030
Alright, alright.

1002
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:53,760
I don't want to ask anymore.

1003
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:56,880
Do whatever you want.

1004
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,770
Thank you, Mother.

1005
00:39:05,030 --> 00:39:05,760
Then I

1006
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:08,200
will have someone propose right away.

1007
00:39:20,490 --> 00:39:24,010
[The Penal Court]

1008
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:34,050
[The Cold Iron Judge]

1009
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,290
How bold of you

1010
00:39:32,510 --> 00:39:34,370
to trespass into the Penal Court.

1011
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:41,180
Your men may be fierce,

1012
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:43,330
but I just said one thing...

1013
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,320
and guess what?

1014
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:46,490
They didn't dare stop me anymore.

1015
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:47,810
What did you say?

1016
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:49,940
I'm considering

1017
00:39:50,110 --> 00:39:52,110
whether to be the Commander's wife.

1018
00:40:06,090 --> 00:40:11,490
[The Cold Iron Judge]

1019
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:07,840
The walls in your office

1020
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:08,970
are too thin.

1021
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:10,280
I can hear

1022
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,480
everything clearly.

1023
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:18,510
Normally, you couldn't.

1024
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:21,580
I had an interrogation room

1025
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:22,920
moved up here.

1026
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:26,960
Good idea.

1027
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,780
You really are different.

1028
00:40:29,530 --> 00:40:30,590
Is there something wrong with you?

1029
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:31,510
I fancy you.

1030
00:40:32,250 --> 00:40:33,320
What is wrong

1031
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,580
with saying it openly?

1032
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:35,990
Why must I hide it?

1033
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,090
What is this?

1034
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,710
This is medicine for my heart condition.

1035
00:40:51,710 --> 00:40:53,240
You have a heart condition?

1036
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:56,630
Since childhood.

1037
00:40:58,590 --> 00:40:59,720
Since the age of six,

1038
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:01,510
I was given all kinds of poison

1039
00:41:01,510 --> 00:41:03,170
under the guise of treatment.

1040
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:05,590
No physician has ever
been able to cure me.

1041
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:06,510
My days

1042
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:08,440
are numbered.

1043
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,230
I heard

1044
00:41:11,150 --> 00:41:12,840
you were widowed once before.

1045
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:15,610
If you've grown fond of being a widow,

1046
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:17,330
then just keep clinging to me.

1047
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:22,840
You asked about me?

1048
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:44,400
You're interested in me too,

1049
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,110
aren't you?

1050
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:47,510
Get out.

1051
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:05,320
Ye Xian.

1052
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:10,280
Do you like Gu Jinzhao?

1053
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,650
I had someone look into it.

1054
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,960
You've had a cold temperament
since childhood

1055
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:19,670
and never liked getting close to others.

1056
00:42:19,670 --> 00:42:22,200
Yet you alone kept
in contact with Gu Jinzhao.

1057
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:24,890
You even helped her raise

1058
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:25,800
a cat.

1059
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:28,630
Get lost.

1060
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:30,060
[The Cold Iron Judge]

1061
00:42:29,030 --> 00:42:29,670
Get lost!

1062
00:43:01,990 --> 00:43:05,640
[A Splendid Match]

